data.description: Cozy Suburban Home: Nestled on a large corner lot in a family-friendly neighborhood, this charming home exudes warmth and comfort. The welcoming front porch invites you to relax and enjoy the peaceful surroundings. Inside, you'll find 3 bedroom (one room does not have a closet) 2 bathroom a recently renovated interior with new flooring, a remodeled kitchen, and plenty of natural light. The backyard features a gazebo, cement patio, sprinkler box/controls and is ready to be landscaped to your liking. With schools and parks nearby, this home is ideal for families looking for their first home and looking for suburban bliss.
